{"tid":2099563,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"手足逼爆旁聽席 法庭再增直播區","createTime":"2020-07-08T10:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T11:05:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"abf089f44ef8c112af94689575b3b164edcc3b66","tid":2099563,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:20:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200708/775ZU5UYEBNMKHJSIMLELGGGHA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200708%2F775ZU5UYEBNMKHJSIMLELGGGHA%2F&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=5241b03a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200708%2F775ZU5UYEBNMKHJSIMLELGGGHA%2F&h=e47dffb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200708/775ZU5UYEBNMKHJSIMLELGGGHA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n手足逼爆旁聽席 法庭再增直播區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/W8yPcYm-XymbxdTvBh1zZZHXe3M=/190x117/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/B6NKGYQONSHSJSGBSKGHRQDV4E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FW8yPcYm-XymbxdTvBh1zZZHXe3M%3D%2F190x117%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FB6NKGYQONSHSJSGBSKGHRQDV4E.jpg&h=55542641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法庭每逢審理抗爭案，均有大批市民到場旁聽及聲援。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】近期抗爭者的提堂案件不絕於耳，「旁聽師」紛紛到場聲援手足。由於法庭旁聽座位有限，常見逾百人到場輪籌逼爆法院。司法機構有見旁聽席供不應求，早前已開始提供直播設施。司法機構本月回覆立法會司法及法律事務委員會指，正根據不同法院大樓的實際需要，分階段增設直播設施，未來數月會令全部裁判法院均備有直播設施。<br />\n<br />\n司法機構表示，留意到越來越多法庭案件、特別是與社會事件有關的案件，有眾多法庭使用者到庭，包括訴訟人、法律代表、與訟人的家人、傳媒和公眾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n涵蓋全部裁判法院<br />\n<br />\n為此司法機構已在終審法院<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n的區院法庭等。<br />\n<br />\n司法機構正根據不同法院<br />\n。。。。<br />\n考慮會否再增設。<br />\n<br />\n================<br />\n<br />\n多謝手足旁聽師<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家要抽時間去支持手足呀，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n沒有暴徒，只有暴政<br />\n沒有送頭，只有濫捕<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece45f1cda451d2a3c188a2a11948ec0a684284a","tid":2099563,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:21:08.000Z","msg":"大家要抽時間去支持手足呀，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n沒有暴徒，只有暴政<br />\n沒有送頭，只有濫捕<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足不是 condom"},{"pid":"b1b6feb4b08acb197ef9018262ee2b867f13ac84","tid":2099563,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />